Source: mcctl
Maintainer: Anton Ekblad <anton@ekblad.cc>
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)

Package: mcctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A daemon to manage Minecraft servers robustly and efficiently.
  Starts and stops your Minecraft server on system boot or shutdown, restarts
  it when it crashes, runs commands without any hassle and generally makes
  running a Minecraft server less painful.
